item.title: Models made with metaseq
item.dc:creator: @the_wanderer The Wanderer
item.description:
@the_wanderer wrote:

[quote=“Cole1497, post:5, topic:383822”][quote author=h1 sk1ller link=topic=479588.msg3511519#msg3511519 date=1298605291]

Wireframe?
Also, if you’re making these for the thread about making LoZ models, there’s a thread for it to post these.

I was thinking the same thing. These really look like models from LoZ.

Because they are…
[/quote]
It’s not like he’s The Wanderer, it’s hard to tell exactly. A quiver and a blue sword with a yellow centerpiece.[/quote]
:’) It’s only because I’m a perfectionist. Hate not having references to get it exact.
